Defendant David M. Mobley Sr., Sr. resides in Naples, Florida.
Mobley Sr. owns and/or controls, directly or indirectly, the other Defendants.
Mobley Sr. has provided sworn testimony to the Commission and the Securities and Exchange Commission in which he has admitted conceiving and carrying out the fraud described in this Complaint.
From time to time during the relevant period, Mobley Sr. transacted business in the Southern District of New York, including but not limited to, maintaining investor funds and
