Ensign maintains an office at P.O. Box 10656, APO, Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands.
Ensign was a vehicle used to receive funds from MIF, MIHF and otherwise, which it used to trade, among other things, commodity futures and options.
From time to time during the relevant period, Ensign has transacted business in the Southern District of New York, including, but not limited to, maintaining customer funds and trading accounts at Morgan Stanley Dean Witter 
17.
