("IAM") is a Bahamian corporation that purportedly acts as a trading manager for Ensign, and is owned and controlled, directly or indirectly, by Mobley Sr. From time to time during the relevant period, MIIC transacted business in the Southern District of New York, including, but not limited to, maintaining investor funds and a trading account at Morgan Stanley Dean Witter 
